### Test Custom Authorization System - Admin Only Features

@host = https://localhost:7038
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api

### 1. Login with regular user (should not be able to access admin endpoints)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "regularuser@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login with Admin user (should be able to access all endpoints)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "Admin045@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### 3. Test Public About endpoint (no authentication required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/about

### 4. Test Protected About Creation (Admin only) - Replace with Admin token
POST {{baseUrl}}/about
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Admin Authorization",
    "description": "This endpoint should only be accessible by users with IsAdmin = true."
}

### 5. Test Protected About Creation with regular user token (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/about
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REGULAR_USER_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Regular User",
    "description": "This should fail because user is not admin."
}

### 6. Test Protected Product Creation (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Test Product - Admin Authorization
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

Testing admin-only product creation
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

25.99
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Stock"

5
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryId"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

### 7. Test Settings Update (Admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/settings/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Updated by Admin Only",
    "phoneNumber": "+1-999-999-9999",
    "email": "admin-updated@ayyuazstore.com",
    "address": "Admin Updated Address"
}

### 8. Test File Upload (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/filestorage/upload
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

[Binary file content]
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Folder"

test
--WebAppBoundary--

### 9. Test Order Management (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Test authenticated but not admin endpoint (any authenticated user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_REGULAR_USER_TOKEN_HERE